def colour_green(x):
  if x<=0:
    color="green"
  elif (x>0) and (x<100):
    color='yellow'
  else:
    color="red"
    #color is 'green' if x<= 0 else "white"
  return 'color:'+ color

cd_c10.style.applymap(colour_green)
cd_c10.style.highlight_min(color='green').highlight_max(color='red')

  ismax=(x==x.max())

def occupied_na(n,d):
  if n==NaN:
    if d==NaN:
      return "N"
    else:
      return "Y"
  else:
    return 'Y'

df.Occupied.apply(occupied_na(df.Num_Students,))
